    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>什么是《太空工程师2》？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《太空工程师2》是一款以工程与殖民为主题的沙盒游戏。你将在完全可破坏的世界中建造飞船、空间站和行星基地，同时跟随米罗与伊万·索科尔的冒险故事，拓展人类在阿尔马盖斯特星系的立足点，并为生存而战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你随人类首次大规模殖民任务抵达遥远的**阿尔马盖斯特星系**。飞船在进入时受损，工具简陋，下方行星虽美却残酷无情。从此刻起，一切建造皆由你掌控。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索殖民星系，开采资源，建造基地与星际飞船，完成合约并开拓疆域——初期独自奋战，后续更可通过抢先体验阶段推出的合作模式与大型多人游戏与好友并肩作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/b5b9cebf8cdcb2fbf3c1712eddadf1cc.poster.avif?t=1764615043\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/b5b9cebf8cdcb2fbf3c1712eddadf1cc.webm?t=1764615043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/b5b9cebf8cdcb2fbf3c1712eddadf1cc.mp4?t=1764615043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创造和毁灭的感觉从未如此美妙</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >太空工程师 2》吸收了我们在过去 10 年中所学到的一切，以前所未有的深度和创造自由度重新打造了太空工程体验。在全新 VRAGE3 引擎的支持下，创造和破坏的感觉前所未有的好。无论您是游戏老手还是新手，《太空工程师 2》都将为您提供一个广阔、引人入胜的沙盒，让您的创造力在这里真正大放异彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/a5027cc80168fa1c42458767402d8355.poster.avif?t=1764615043\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/a5027cc80168fa1c42458767402d8355.webm?t=1764615043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精准建造</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索新一代建筑技术！使用全新的 25 厘米统一网格系统，以惊人的精度搭建你能想象到的任何东西。不再有大网格和小网格之分--积木可以无缝地拼接在一起，让复杂的搭建变得更加容易。安装点可视化和网格线使建造比以往更加直观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/bbd23010ebcf8ab2a062f965630bf182.poster.avif?t=1764615043\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/bbd23010ebcf8ab2a062f965630bf182.webm?t=1764615043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>增强控制和移动性</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的新系统包括网格撤销和改进的 CTRL 控制，可实现精确旋转和缩放，确保每一步都能进行直观的设计。通过升级的最大速度，让您的创作达到新的速度：字符速度高达 310 米/秒，网格速度高达 300 米/秒。您不必担心会从平台或小行星上掉下来--磁靴和自动喷气背包会帮您解决后顾之忧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/ae855833ff805e16f435448b13f9b83c.poster.avif?t=1764615043\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/ae855833ff805e16f435448b13f9b83c.webm?t=1764615043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/ae855833ff805e16f435448b13f9b83c.mp4?t=1764615043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>更智能的用户界面和更流畅的游戏体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们重新设计了用户界面/用户体验，让新手和专业玩家都能更顺畅、更直观地构建游戏，让您更自由地将复杂的想法变为现实。得益于 VRAGE3，《太空工程师 2》将提供更好的性能，让您玩得更顺畅。随着早期接入的推进，您将能够建造更大的飞船，驾驶更多的飞船，在真正身临其境的体验中享受史诗般的破坏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/b8320a7d13f6170708cfc205a4028b8d.poster.avif?t=1764615043\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/b8320a7d13f6170708cfc205a4028b8d.webm?t=1764615043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>顶级视觉效果</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受太空之美、工业设计和战斗场面，这些都是以全新的逼真度重新打造的。在《太空工程师 2》中，我们引入了全新的光线追踪全局照明、逼真的阴影、全新的天空盒、细分体素材质、装甲视差效果等，为每个场景带来深度和真实感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/2e438a0c0b775bee659c8b68d32d96d7.poster.avif?t=1764615043\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1133870/extras/2e438a0c0b775bee659c8b68d32d96d7.webm?t=1764615043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
